the union leader to the towering solidarity workers monument outside 
the lenin shipyards 
walesa in an interview monday said poland is making progress 
with its political freedoms faster than it is tackling its economic 
problems 
he said he wants bush to help us make this correction so that 
financial matters are addressed with the same emphasis as political 
affairs 
crowned by three crosses topped with anchors the solidarity 
monument commemorates the first three shipyard workers killed by 
