<TEXT>
two bombs exploded in mecca as thousands 
of people took part in the annual pilgrimage to islams most sacred 
city killing one person and injuring 16 the official saudi press 
said today 
two of the injured are in critical condition the saudi news 
agency said quoting an unnamed saudi interior ministry security 
official 
